// pending л∞∞мєШмЭШ мГБмДЄл•Љ нММмЛ±нХі мЪФмХљ нФДл°ђнФДнКЄ мГЭмД±. (мЧ∞м∞® нХДнД∞лКФ мИШмІСкЄ∞л°Ь мЭілПЩлР®)
// [All Items] SELECT к≤∞к≥Љ(rows)мЩА мГБмДЄм°∞нЪМ($input)л•Љ мЭЄлН±мК§л°Ь мІЭмІУлКФлЛ§.
const rows = $('pending л∞∞мєШ м°∞нЪМ').all();
const details = $input.all();
const out = [];
for (let i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
  const r = rows[i].json;
  const d = details[i]?.json || {};
  let responsibility = '', qualifications = '', preferred = '', ok = true;
  if (d.result) {
    responsibility = d.result.responsibility || '';
    qualifications = d.result.qualifications || '';
    preferred      = d.result.preferredRequirements || '';
  } else if (d.data?.job?.detail) {
    const det = d.data.job.detail;
    responsibility = det.main_tasks || det.intro || '';
    qualifications = det.requirements || '';
    preferred      = det.preferred_points || '';
  } else { ok = false; }                  // мГБмДЄ нММмЛ± мЛ§нМ® вЖТ fail

  const action = ok ? 'summarize' : 'fail';
  const prompt = `м†Ьл™©: ${r.title}\nнЪМмВђ: ${r.company}\n\n[м£ЉмЪФмЧЕлђі]\n${responsibility}\n\n[мЮРк≤©мЪФк±і]\n${qualifications}\n\n[мЪ∞лМАмВђнХ≠]\n${preferred}`;
  out.push({ json: { id: r.id, source: r.source, job_id: r.job_id, company: r.company, title: r.title, url: r.url, attempts: r.attempts, action, prompt } });
}
return out;

// мЪФмХљ мД±к≥µ вЖТ done UPDATE, мЛ§нМ®(лєИ мЭСлЛµ) вЖТ мЮђмЛЬлПД мЇ°. [Each Item]
// (мЧ∞м∞®/кЄ∞мИ†мК§нГЭмЭА мИШмІС лЛ®к≥ДмЧРмДЬ мЭілѓЄ м†АмЮ•лР®. мЪФмХљмЧРмДЬ кЄ∞мИ†мК§нГЭ л≥імЩДлІМ.)
const m = $('м≤Шл¶ђ м§АлєД').item.json;
const content = $json.choices?.[0]?.message?.content;
const esc = (v) => v == null ? 'NULL' : `'${String(v).replace(/'/g, "''")}'`;
const arr = (list) => { const a = (list || []).map(s => `'${String(s).replace(/'/g, "''")}'`); return a.length ? `ARRAY[${a.join(',')}]::text[]` : `'{}'::text[]`; };
let sql;
if (content) {
  let stacks = []; const mm = content.match(/кЄ∞мИ†мК§нГЭ\s*[:пЉЪ]\s*(.+)/);
  if (mm) stacks = mm[1].split(/[,¬Ј]/).map(s => s.trim()).filter(Boolean);
  // мИШмІС лХМ м±ДмЪі tech_stacksк∞А мЮИмЬЉл©і мЬ†мІА, мЧЖмЬЉл©і(мЫРнЛ∞лУЬ лУ±) мЪФмХљмЧРмДЬ мґФмґЬнХЬ к≤ГмЬЉл°Ь
  sql = `UPDATE jobs SET status='done', summary=${esc(content)}, tech_stacks=CASE WHEN cardinality(tech_stacks)>0 THEN tech_stacks ELSE ${arr(stacks)} END, attempts=attempts+1, updated_at=now() WHERE source=${esc(m.source)} AND job_id=${esc(m.job_id)};`;
} else {
  const maxAtt = Number($('мД§м†Х (Config)').first().json.maxAttempts) || 3;
  sql = `UPDATE jobs SET status=CASE WHEN attempts+1 >= ${maxAtt} THEN 'failed' ELSE 'pending' END, attempts=attempts+1, updated_at=now() WHERE source=${esc(m.source)} AND job_id=${esc(m.job_id)};`;
}
return { json: { sql } };

// skip(мЧ∞м∞®м†ЬмЩЄ) вЖТ 'skipped', fail(мГБмДЄмЛ§нМ®) вЖТ мЮђмЛЬлПД мЇ°. [Each Item]
const m = $json;
const esc = (v) => v == null ? 'NULL' : `'${String(v).replace(/'/g, "''")}'`;
const maxAtt = Number($('мД§м†Х (Config)').first().json.maxAttempts) || 3;
let sql;
if (m.action === 'skip') {
  sql = `UPDATE jobs SET status='skipped', attempts=attempts+1, updated_at=now() WHERE source=${esc(m.source)} AND job_id=${esc(m.job_id)};`;
} else {
  sql = `UPDATE jobs SET status=CASE WHEN attempts+1 >= ${maxAtt} THEN 'failed' ELSE 'pending' END, attempts=attempts+1, updated_at=now() WHERE source=${esc(m.source)} AND job_id=${esc(m.job_id)};`;
}
return { json: { sql } };
